[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Pagebanner default.jpg"]]},"\n",{"type":"'''","value":["Porthcawl"]}," is a small seaside town in Mid Glamorgan, South Wales.\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n",{"type":"===","value":["Seaside"]},"\nPortcawl is a traditional holiday resort and in its heyday its beaches were very popular with holiday makers from the nearby south Wales valleys.  Beaches include:\n",{"type":"*","value":["Trecco Bay"]},{"type":"*","value":["Rest Bay"]},{"type":"*","value":["Coney Beach"]},"\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\nConey Beach features a traditional fairground complete with amusement arcades. \n\n",{"type":"===","value":["Golf"]},"\nPortcawl has some excellent golf courses:\n",{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Grove Golf Club"],["alt="],["url=http:\/\/www.grovegolf.com\/"],["email="],["address="],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone =+44 1656 788-771"],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=South Cornelly, Nr Porthcawl, Bridgend, CF33 4RP. 6128 yard, 18 hole, par 70 course"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Royal Porthcawl Golf Club"],["alt="],["url=http:\/\/www.royalporthcawl.com\/"],["email="],["address="],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone =+44 1656 782-251"],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=Rest Bay, Porthcawl, CF36 3UW. 18 hole, 6870 yard, par 72 links course beside the sea with a panoramic view of Swansea Bay"]]}]},{"type":"*","value":[" ",{"type":"{{","value":[["do"],["name=Pyle and Kenfig Golf Club"],["alt="],["url=http:\/\/www.pandkgolfclub.co.uk\/"],["email="],["address="],["lat="],["long="],["directions="],["phone =+44 1656 783-093"],["tollfree="],["fax="],["hours="],["price="],["content=Waun-y-Mer, Kenfig CF33 4PU. 18 hole, par 71, 6728 yard links course."]]}]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Buy"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Ea